msgstr "TODO テクスチャヒーリングを有効にする"

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "Nix wrapper paths"
msgstr "Nixラッパーのパス"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:68
msgid ""
"The Nix Emacs wrapper (=extraEmacsPackages=) adds binaries to =exec-path= "
"that are absent from the shell's =PATH=.  Both exec-path-from-shell and "
"envrc replace =exec-path= during operation, losing these entries.  Capturing "
"them once at init allows both packages to merge them back."
msgstr ""
"NixのEmacsラッパー（=extraEmacsPackages=）は、シェルの =PATH= に 存在しないバ"
"イナリを =exec-path= に追加します。 exec-path-from-shellとenvrcはどちらも動作"
"時に =exec-path= を 置き換えるため、これらのエントリが失われます。 初期化時に"
"一度保存しておくことで、両パッケージから マージし直せるようにしています。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:75
#, no-wrap
msgid "(setq my/nix-exec-path exec-path)"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "Darwin"
msgstr "Darwin"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:79
msgid ""
"On macOS, Emacs cannot inherit environment variables (such as ~$PATH~) from "
"the shell, so [[https://github.com/purcell/exec-path-from-shell][exec-path-"
"from-shell]] is needed as a workaround.  [[https://github.com/d12frosted/"
"homebrew-emacs-plus/blob/3e61ee44f4cfc43dce292047aff5e9277e7d1bd4/Library/"
"EmacsBase.rb#L33-L49][emacs-plus]] injects PATH into Emacs's Info.plist, so "
"applying that patch might eliminate the need for this package."
msgstr ""
"macOSでは、Emacsはシェルから環境変数（~$PATH~ など）を 継承できないため、回避"
"策として [[https://github.com/purcell/exec-path-from-shell][exec-path-from-"
"shell]]が 必要です。 [[https://github.com/d12frosted/homebrew-emacs-plus/"
"blob/3e61ee44f4cfc43dce292047aff5e9277e7d1bd4/Library/EmacsBase.rb#L33-L49]"
"[emacs-plus]]は PATHをEmacsのInfo.plistに注入するため、そのパッチを 適用すれ"
"ばこのパッケージは不要になるかもしれません。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:83
msgid ""
"=exec-path-from-shell-initialize= replaces =exec-path= with the login "
"shell's ~PATH~.  Merging =my/nix-exec-path= back after initialization "
"preserves wrapper-provided paths."
msgstr ""
"=exec-path-from-shell-initialize= はログインシェルの ~PATH~ で =exec-path= を"
"置き換えます。初期化後に =my/nix-exec-path= を マージし直すことで、ラッパー由"
"来のパスを保持します。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:87
msgid ""
"When launched from an application launcher (Dock, Spotlight), Emacs inherits "
"only the minimal launchd environment, which lacks Nix-related variables. "
"Without these, =direnv export= may produce incomplete results. ([[https://"
"github.com/purcell/envrc/issues/92][envrc#92]])"
msgstr ""
"アプリケーションランチャー（Dock、Spotlight）から起動した場合、 EmacsはNix関"
"連の変数を含まない最小限のlaunchd環境のみを 継承します。これらがないと "
"=direnv export= が不完全な結果を 返すことがあります。 （[[https://github.com/"
"purcell/envrc/issues/92][envrc#92]]）"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:92
msgid ""
"Separately, fish sources =conf.d/*.fish= even for non-interactive "
"invocations (=fish -c \"...\"=). nix-darwin places environment setup scripts "
"there that re-initialize PATH from system profiles when guard variables "
"(=__fish_nixos_env_preinit_sourced=, =__NIX_DARWIN_SET_ENVIRONMENT_DONE=, "
"=__HM_SESS_VARS_SOURCED=) are absent. Without propagating these guards, "
"subprocesses spawned by =compile= or =shell-command= lose the buffer-local "
"PATH that envrc constructed—even though envrc itself applied the correct "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"また、fishは非対話的な呼び出し（=fish -c \"...\"=）でも =conf.d/*.fish= を読"
"み込みます。nix-darwinはそこに環境セットアップ スクリプトを配置しており、ガー"
"ド変数 （=__fish_nixos_env_preinit_sourced=、 "
"=__NIX_DARWIN_SET_ENVIRONMENT_DONE=、 =__HM_SESS_VARS_SOURCED=）がない場合、 "
"システムプロファイルからPATHを再初期化します。 これらのガード変数を伝播しない"
"と、 =compile= や =shell-command= が生成するサブプロセスは、 envrc自体は正し"
"い環境を適用していたにもかかわらず、 envrcが構築したバッファローカルのPATHを"
"失います。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:102
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package exec-path-from-shell\n"
"  :ensure t\n"
"  :config\n"
"  (when (memq window-system '(mac ns x))\n"
"    (dolist (var '(\"SSH_AUTH_SOCK\" \"SSH_AGENT_PID\" \"GPG_AGENT_INFO\"\n"
"                   \"LANG\" \"LC_CTYPE\" \"NIX_SSL_CERT_FILE\" \"NIX_PATH\"\n"
"                   \"__fish_nixos_env_preinit_sourced\"\n"
"                   \"__NIX_DARWIN_SET_ENVIRONMENT_DONE\"\n"
"                   \"__HM_SESS_VARS_SOURCED\"))\n"
"      (add-to-list 'exec-path-from-shell-variables var))\n"
"    (exec-path-from-shell-initialize)\n"
"    (setq exec-path (delete-dups (append exec-path my/nix-exec-path)))))"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "envrc"
msgstr "envrc"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:118
msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/purcell/envrc][envrc.el]] provides buffer-local "
"environment variables based on direnv. This enables Emacs to recognize "
"project-specific development environments managed by direnv."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/purcell/envrc][envrc.el]]はdirenvに基づく バッファローカ"
"ルの環境変数を提供します。これにより、Emacsが direnvで管理されたプロジェクト"
"固有の開発環境を 認識できるようになります。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:122
msgid ""
"Unlike direnv.el which sets environment variables globally, envrc.el keeps "
"them buffer-local. This is essential when working on multiple projects "
"simultaneously, each with its own .envrc."
msgstr ""
"環境変数をグローバルに設定するdirenv.elとは異なり、envrc.elは バッファローカ"
"ルに保持します。それぞれ独自の.envrcを持つ 複数のプロジェクトを同時に扱う場合"
"に不可欠です。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:126
msgid ""
"The mode must be enabled early (via after-init hook) so that other packages "
"can inherit the correct environment."
msgstr ""
"他のパッケージが正しい環境を継承できるよう、このモードは 早期に（after-init"
"フックで）有効にする必要があります。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:129
msgid ""
"When envrc updates a buffer's environment, it replaces =exec-path= with "
"values from =direnv export=, losing the Nix wrapper paths.  ([[https://"
"github.com/purcell/envrc/issues/9][envrc#9]])  Merging =my/nix-exec-path= "
"back after each update preserves access to wrapper-provided executables "
"(e.g. yaml-language-server)  inside direnv-managed buffers."
msgstr ""
"envrcがバッファの環境を更新すると、=exec-path= を =direnv export= の値で置き"
"換え、Nixラッパーのパスが 失われます。 （[[https://github.com/purcell/envrc/"
"issues/9][envrc#9]]） 更新のたびに =my/nix-exec-path= をマージし直すことで、 "
"direnv管理下のバッファ内でラッパー由来の実行ファイル （例: yaml-language-"
"server）へのアクセスを保持します。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:138
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package envrc\n"
"  :ensure t\n"
"  :hook (after-init . envrc-global-mode)\n"
"  :config\n"
"  (advice-add 'envrc--update :after\n"
"    (defun my/envrc-preserve-nix-path (&rest _)\n"
"      (when (local-variable-p 'exec-path)\n"
"        (setq-local exec-path\n"
"                    (delete-dups (append exec-path my/nix-exec-path)))))))"
msgstr ""

