"ルリクエストのレビュー、 通知の管理が行えます。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:292
msgid ""
"Forge authenticates via =ghub=, which reads credentials from =auth-"
"sources=.  The =authinfo.age= file should contain a GitHub API token entry:"
msgstr ""
"Forgeは =ghub= を通じて認証を行い、 =auth-sources= から認証情報を読み取りま"
"す。 =authinfo.age= ファイルにはGitHub APIトークンの エントリを記載する必要が"
"あります:"

#. type: paragraph in example
#: applications/emacs/init.org:296
#, no-wrap
msgid "machine api.github.com login <username>^forge password <token>"
msgstr "machine api.github.com login <username>^forge password <token>"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:299
msgid ""
"The token is a fine-grained personal access token with a 6-month expiration "
"that requires periodic regeneration.  The required permissions are:"
msgstr ""
"トークンは有効期限6ヶ月のfine-grainedパーソナルアクセストークンで、 定期的な"
"再生成が必要です。必要な権限は以下の通りです:"

#. type: plain list -
#: applications/emacs/init.org:304
#, no-wrap
msgid "Issues: Read and Write"
msgstr "Issues: Read and Write"

#. type: plain list -
#: applications/emacs/init.org:305
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pull requests: Read and Write"
msgstr "Pull requests: Read and Write"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:307
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package forge\n"
"  :ensure t\n"
