#: applications/emacs/init.org:344
#, no-wrap
msgid "tree-sitter"
msgstr "tree-sitter"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:346
msgid "Use maximum font-lock level for tree-sitter modes."
msgstr "tree-sitterモードでfont-lockレベルを最大にします。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:349
#, no-wrap
msgid "(setq treesit-font-lock-level 4)"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:352
#, no-wrap
msgid "Markdown"
msgstr "Markdown"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:354
msgid "https://github.com/jrblevin/markdown-mode"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in quote
#: applications/emacs/init.org:357
msgid "markdown-mode is a major mode for editing Markdown-formatted text."
msgstr ""
"markdown-modeはMarkdown形式のテキストを編集するためのメジャーモードです。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:361
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package markdown-mode\n"
"  :ensure t\n"
"  :mode (\"README\\\\.md\\\\'\" . gfm-mode)\n"
"  :init (setq markdown-command \"multimarkdown\")\n"
"  :bind (:map markdown-mode-map\n"
"              (\"C-c C-e\" . markdown-do)))"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:371
msgid "https://github.com/nix-community/nix-ts-mode"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:373
msgid "Tree-sitter based major mode for Nix expressions."
msgstr "Nix式のためのtree-sitterベースのメジャーモードです。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:375
msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/nix-community/nixd][nixd]] (configured via lsp-mode) "
"provides IDE features for Nix expressions by interoperating with the C++ Nix "
"evaluator.  Unlike nil which relies on static analysis, nixd performs actual "
"Nix evaluation, enabling accurate completion for attribute paths (e.g. "
"=pkgs.=), NixOS options, and flake inputs."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/nix-community/nixd][nixd]]（lsp-mode経由で設定） はC++の"
"Nixエバリュエーターと連携し、Nix式のIDE機能を提供します。 静的解析に頼るnilと"
"は異なり、nixdは実際のNix評価を行うため、 属性パス（例: =pkgs.=）やNixOSオプ"
"ション、 flakeの入力に対する正確な補完が可能です。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:383
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package nix-ts-mode\n"
"  :ensure t\n"
"  :mode \"\\\\.nix\\\\'\"\n"
"  :hook (nix-ts-mode . lsp-deferred)\n"
"  :init\n"
"  ;; org-src-lang-modes is defined in org-src, which may not be loaded yet at init time\n"
"  (with-eval-after-load 'org-src\n"
"    (add-to-list 'org-src-lang-modes '(\"nix\" . nix-ts)))\n"
"  :config\n"
"  (setq lsp-nix-nixd-formatting-command [\"nixfmt\"]))"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:395
#, no-wrap
msgid "Terraform"
msgstr "Terraform"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:397
msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/hcl-emacs/terraform-mode][terraform-mode]] provides "
"syntax highlighting and indentation for Terraform (HCL) files."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/hcl-emacs/terraform-mode][terraform-mode]]は Terraform"
"（HCL）ファイルのシンタックスハイライトと インデントを提供します。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:399
msgid ""
"No tree-sitter variant is available in MELPA, so using the traditional major "
"mode."
msgstr ""
"tree-sitter版はMELPAで提供されていないため、従来の メジャーモードを使用してい"
"ます。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:402
msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-ls][terraform-ls]] (configured via "
"lsp-mode) provides IDE features such as completion, diagnostics via "
"=terraform validate=, and go-to-definition for Terraform configurations."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform-ls][terraform-ls]] （lsp-mode経由で"
"設定）は、補完、=terraform validate= による診断、 Terraform設定に対する定義"
"ジャンプなどのIDE機能を提供します。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:407
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package terraform-mode\n"
"  :ensure t\n"
"  :hook (terraform-mode . lsp-deferred))"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:412
#, no-wrap
msgid "PO"
msgstr "PO"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:414
msgid ""
"[[https://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/manual/html_node/PO-Mode.html][po-"
"mode]] is Emacs's major mode for editing GNU gettext PO (Portable Object) "
"files.  PO files store translations for software internationalization."
msgstr ""
"[[https://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/manual/html_node/PO-Mode.html][po-"
"mode]]は GNU gettext PO（Portable Object）ファイルを編集するための Emacsのメ"
"ジャーモードです。POファイルはソフトウェアの 国際化のための翻訳を格納します。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:417
msgid ""
"Editing PO files as plain text is error-prone because the format has strict "
"requirements for escaping and structure.  po-mode provides structured "
"navigation between entries, automatic validation, and prevents common "
"formatting errors."
msgstr ""
"POファイルをプレーンテキストとして編集するのはエラーが 起きやすく、エスケープ"
"や構造に厳格な要件があるためです。 po-modeはエントリ間の構造化されたナビゲー"
"ション、 自動バリデーション、よくあるフォーマットエラーの防止を 提供します。"

#. type: heading ***
#: applications/emacs/init.org:422
#, no-wrap
msgid "Common Operations"
msgstr "共通の操作"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:424
msgid ""
"PO mode is not derived from text mode.  The buffer is read-only and has its "
"own keymap, so standard text editing commands do not work directly.  "
"Translations must be edited through the subedit buffer (=RET=)."
msgstr ""
"PO modeはtext modeから派生していません。バッファは読み取り専用で 独自のキー"
"マップを持つため、通常のテキスト編集コマンドは 直接使えません。翻訳はサブエ"
"ディットバッファ（=RET=）を 通じて編集する必要があります。"

