msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/emacsattic/protobuf-ts-mode][protobuf-ts-mode]] is a "
"tree-sitter-based major mode for editing proto3 files."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/emacsattic/protobuf-ts-mode][protobuf-ts-mode]]は proto3"
"ファイルを編集するためのtree-sitterベースの メジャーモードです。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:482
msgid ""
"The mode auto-registers =.proto= files when the =proto= grammar is available."
msgstr ""
"=proto= グラマーが利用可能な場合、このモードは =.proto= ファイルを自動登録し"
"ます。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:485
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package protobuf-ts-mode\n"
"  :ensure t)"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:489
#, no-wrap
msgid "Justfile"
msgstr "Justfile"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:491
msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/leon-barrett/just-ts-mode.el][just-ts-mode]] is a tree-"
"sitter-based major mode for editing [[https://github.com/casey/just][just]] "
"command runner files.  =C-c '= opens a dedicated editing buffer for the "
"recipe body at point, with automatic shebang-based language detection."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/leon-barrett/just-ts-mode.el][just-ts-mode]]は "
"[[https://github.com/casey/just][just]]コマンドランナーファイルを 編集するた"
"めのtree-sitterベースのメジャーモードです。 =C-c '= でポイント位置のレシピ本"
"文用の専用編集バッファが開き、 shebangに基づく自動言語検出が行われます。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:496
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package just-ts-mode\n"
"  :ensure t)"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:500
#, no-wrap
msgid "YAML"
msgstr "YAML"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:502
msgid ""
"=yaml-ts-mode= is a built-in tree-sitter-based major mode for YAML files.  "
"The tree-sitter grammar is already available via =treesit-grammars.with-all-"
"grammars=, so the mode activates automatically when the grammar is present."
msgstr ""
"=yaml-ts-mode= はYAMLファイル用の組み込みtree-sitterベースの メジャーモードで"
"す。tree-sitterグラマーは =treesit-grammars.with-all-grammars= で既に利用可能"
"なため、 グラマーが存在すればモードは自動で有効になります。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:506
msgid ""
"yaml-language-server (configured via lsp-mode) provides schema validation "
"using [[https://www.schemastore.org/][SchemaStore]].  For example, files "
"under =.github/workflows/= are automatically matched to the GitHub Actions "
"workflow schema, enabling completion and diagnostics for workflow "
"definitions."
msgstr ""
"yaml-language-server（lsp-mode経由で設定）は [[https://www.schemastore.org/]"
"[SchemaStore]]を使った スキーマバリデーションを提供します。例えば、 =.github/"
"workflows/= 配下のファイルはGitHub Actions ワークフロースキーマに自動でマッチ"
"し、 ワークフロー定義の補完と診断が有効になります。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:513
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(use-package yaml-ts-mode\n"
"  :ensure nil\n"
"  :mode (\"\\\\.ya?ml\\\\'\")\n"
"  :hook (yaml-ts-mode . lsp-deferred))"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading *
#: applications/emacs/init.org:519
#, no-wrap
msgid "org"
msgstr "Org"

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:521
#, no-wrap
msgid "Semantic Line Breaks"
msgstr "Semantic Line Breaks"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:523
msgid ""
"[[https://sembr.org/][Semantic Line Breaks (SemBr)]] is a writing convention "
"where line breaks are placed at logical boundaries in sentences, such as "
"after punctuation marks or between phrases.  This makes diffs more "
"meaningful in version control and improves readability without affecting the "
"rendered output."
msgstr ""
"[[https://sembr.org/][Semantic Line Breaks (SemBr)]]は、 句読点の後やフレーズ"
"の間など、文の論理的な境界で 改行を入れる書き方の規約です。これにより、 バー"
"ジョン管理でのdiffがより意味のあるものになり、 レンダリング結果に影響を与えず"
"に可読性が向上します。"

#. type: paragraph
#: applications/emacs/init.org:529
msgid ""
"The recommended line length is around 80 characters.  I set this as an upper "
"limit in the editor to prevent lines from becoming unnecessarily long."
msgstr ""
"推奨される行の長さは約80文字です。行が不必要に 長くなるのを防ぐため、エディタ"
"で上限として設定しています。"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:534
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"(add-hook 'text-mode-hook\n"
"          (lambda ()\n"
"            (auto-fill-mode 1)\n"
"            (setq fill-column 80)))"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading **
#: applications/emacs/init.org:540
#, no-wrap
msgid "org-capture"
msgstr "org-capture"

#. type: paragraph in src
#: applications/emacs/init.org:542
#, no-wrap
