#. type: heading ****
#: modules/configuration.org:673
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pinentry"
msgstr "Pinentry"

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:675
msgid ""
"When connected via SSH, GPG's pinentry is switched to the curses (terminal) "
"variant.  The default graphical pinentry cannot display on a remote session "
"without X11/Wayland forwarding, so the TUI fallback is necessary for signing "
"commits and decrypting secrets over SSH. See [[https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/"
"GnuPG#Changing_pinentry_for_SSH_logins][Gentoo Wiki: GnuPG - Changing "
"pinentry for SSH logins]]."
msgstr ""
"SSH経由で接続している場合、GPGのpinentryをcurses（ターミナル）バリアントに切"
"り替えます。デフォルトのグラフィカルなpinentryはX11/Waylandフォワーディングな"
"しではリモートセッションで表示できないため、SSH経由でのコミット署名やシーク"
"レット復号にTUIのフォールバックが必要です。[[https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/"
"GnuPG#Changing_pinentry_for_SSH_logins][Gentoo Wiki: GnuPG - Changing "
"pinentry for SSH logins]]を参照してください。"

#. type: keyword NAME
#: modules/configuration.org:680
#, no-wrap
msgid "fish-pinentry"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:683
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"if test \"$SSH_CONNECTION\" != \"\"\n"
"  set -x PINENTRY_USER_DATA \"USE_CURSES\"\n"
"end"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading ****
#: modules/configuration.org:688
#, no-wrap
msgid "Extra Abbreviations"
msgstr "追加の略語"

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:690
msgid ""
"Position-aware [[https://fishshell.com/docs/current/cmds/abbr.html]"
"[abbreviations]] that use fish's advanced features (=--position anywhere=, "
"=--regex=, =--function=) which are not available through home-manager's "
"=shellAbbrs= option."
msgstr ""
"位置認識型の[[https://fishshell.com/docs/current/cmds/abbr.html][略語]]で、"
"fishの高度な機能（=--position anywhere=、=--regex=、=--function=）を使用して"
"います。これらはhome-managerの =shellAbbrs= オプションでは利用できません。"

#. type: keyword NAME
#: modules/configuration.org:693
#, no-wrap
msgid "fish-extra-abbrs"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
#: modules/configuration.org:696
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"abbr -a L --position anywhere --set-cursor \"% | less\"\n"
"abbr -a !! --position anywhere --function _abbr_last_history_item\n"
"abbr -a extract_tar_gz --position command --regex \".+\\.tar\\.gz\" --function _abbr_extract_tar_gz\n"
"abbr -a dotdot --regex '^\\.\\.+$' --function _abbr_multicd"
msgstr ""

#. type: heading ****
#: modules/configuration.org:702
#, no-wrap
msgid "any-nix-shell"
msgstr "any-nix-shell"

#. type: paragraph
#: modules/configuration.org:704
msgid ""
"[[https://github.com/haslersn/any-nix-shell][any-nix-shell]] keeps fish as "
"the interactive shell inside =nix shell= and =nix develop= environments. "
"Without it, entering a Nix shell drops into bash (the default builder "
"shell), losing fish's interactive features. This is sourced at the end of "
"=interactiveShellInit= so it can wrap the shell entry point after all other "
"configuration is applied."
msgstr ""
"[[https://github.com/haslersn/any-nix-shell][any-nix-shell]]は=nix shell= や "
"=nix develop= 環境内でfishを対話的シェルとして維持します。これがないと、Nix"
"シェルに入る際にbash（デフォルトのビルダーシェル）に落ち、fishの対話機能が失"
"われます。他のすべての設定が適用された後にシェルのエントリーポイントをラップ"
"できるよう、=interactiveShellInit= の末尾でソースされます。"

#. type: keyword NAME
#: modules/configuration.org:710
#, no-wrap
msgid "fish-any-nix-shell"
msgstr ""

#. type: paragraph in src
